data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Back on the market buyer financing fell through!! SELLER MOTIVATED!    Here is your opportunity to own your perfect Florida Dream Home! This three-bedroom two-bathroom home has over 1700 square feet, from the moment you enter the foyer you will be greeted by a Formal Dining Room, with entryway to Kitchen for easy entertaining. This open concept floor plan features flat island Kitchen & Stainless-steel appliances.   From the family room you can walk out to covered lanai & backyard. Master Suite features walk in closet, double sinks in Master Bath plus walk in shower with glass enclosure.   Separate and convenient laundry room.  Come by and check this amazing Cypress Oaks community, amenities include a large community pool, playground, dog park, and direct access to the South Lake Trail runs in front of the community to enjoy that hiking/biking/walking that makes Groveland/Clermont such an amazing place to live!!  Close access to the turnpike and Highway 50. Community Minutes from major Highways, Restaurants, Hospital, Medical Offices, Major Grocery and Retail Stores, Movie Theater and much more.
